cs.CR, cs.IR, cs.NI, cs.SE, cs.SY

The paper discusses security and privacy issues in IoT systems, which are related to computer security (cs.CR), information retrieval (cs.IR), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), software engineering (cs.SE), and systems and control (cs.SY). However, since the focus of the paper is on security, cs.CR is the most likely sub-category.
